  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "2. Toast the bread until lightly browned.",
    "3. Butter the toasted bread.",
    "4. In a bowl, whisk together eggs, salt, and black pepper.",
    "5. Add minced garlic to the egg mixture.",
    "6. Pour the egg mixture over the toasted bread.",
    "7. Sprinkle cheddar cheese over the top.",
    "8. Bake in the oven for 10-12 minutes, or until the cheese is melted and bubbly.",
    "9. Remove from the oven and let cool for a few minutes.",
    "10. Serve warm."
